---
title: Sri Lankan Banana Blossom Curry with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Traditionally used in Southeast Asian cooking and with a similar texture to cooked white fish, banana blossom is the perfect plant-based substitute for a classic Sri Lankan-style rice and curry bowl. Packed to the brim with nutritious veggies and crushed peanuts, you'll be glad you trusted us and tried this banging delight.
